{"type": "article", "id": 13575, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-17T08:04:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14594, "name": "电动滑板"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 14595, "name": "宠物居所"}, {"id": 2559, "name": "花瓶"}, {"id": 12826, "name": "厨房用品"}, {"id": 14596, "name": "工具盒子"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000241UjHcAxM2WpmeIlz1.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tILĀ by Sunday Suppers\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>ILĀ 是 Sunday Suppers 推出的一整套厨房调味品，包括橄榄油、各种香料、不同种类的盐等。这些产品的原料是由 Sunday Suppers 从世界各地优秀的原料生产地搜集而来，从种植到收获，再到最后的成品，都处在团队严格的监控和把关之下，是非常自然健康的厨房材料。另外，Sunday Suppers 为他们的产品设计了简洁但非常个性化的外包装，光是看着就觉得进厨房以及与家人朋友共同进餐是件特别美妙的事情。<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/180473509/ila-essentials-for-a-beautiful-home-by-sunday-supp\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141302a0Xu6RCQy1VeFqSd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79677419\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203038C1YgA6L7Xo5jM9GV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33870968\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141303JQ6FZkAliCmB0Hcp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141304CqEkfmwTOYW4JZAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203038ZAirmqFs6kGENDY3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141304HF9sce7PTNvRgym4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203039qdVheQPL2XTYZry7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59354839\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203040oltf3AYK6IDPnRbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203040NeQ8lk16f2XdzS0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tO2 Vase by ODDD<span> </span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是来自伦敦的设计工作室 ODDD 推出的一系列花瓶，意在体味 2D 和 3D 之间奇妙的转换。只需要折叠纸张并充气，就可以完成花瓶的手工制作，是不是有点像我们小时候做的手工，不过它们使用的是防水材料，可以真正装上水，插进鲜花。另外还有两款花瓶采用高密度聚乙烯合成纸材质，不可见水，专门为干花设计。另外，花瓶表面还设计了金属箔片，看上去有 “blingbling” 的效果。<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/505844910/o2-vase\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052030417oj8tI0nrRxWwVBa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203041RakdX9gDpeYfyqmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052030412kbJGglhmqoOKY3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.82640587\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203042xDCXaM6zlsdw5bmN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203042bAr0XFRYML8cv4Nd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62836186\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203043TnWVdXcSZqtF87Me.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203043wjvxCh2nHB1IfJQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203045tQWbog8dEkcpZ1lK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tJapanese Cedar Carpenter’s Box by Best Made Co\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>日本优质工具品牌 Best Made Co 最近推出了一个叫做 “Japanese Cedar Carpenter’s Box” 的工具盒子，采用柳杉制作而成，兼具简洁的设计和精巧的工匠手艺。盒子平面抽拉门平滑稳定，无缝防水。同时，盒子进行了抗菌防虫处理，避免盒子受潮或者久置后遭遇细菌蚊虫的侵袭。同时，因为所用木材纹理的区别，每一只盒子都是世界上独一无二的。<a href=\"http://www.bestmadeco.com/collections/this-week-at-best-made/products/japanese-cedar-carpenters-box#product-tab\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203046Pp5rc8MKq09u7lQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203046GZFPbl8KIcrS5g4w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203047JeoWnISaEQ47RqLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203047CQvBJjIwPg93uFR6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tNiku Rug by Ma Yansong \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>此前，日本设计大师原研哉在全世界发起了名为“设计：为了爱犬”的展览策划，号召来自世界各地的设计师，建筑师为狗狗设计居所。近日，马岩松发布了作品 “Niku Rug”，由三个手工编织褥垫组成，这个犬居专门为拉布拉多犬打造，因为拉布拉多喜食肉，因此 “Niku Rug” 用了深浅不一的编制来凸显肉的纹理，让拉布拉多爱上这个开放性的小居所。展览于 8 月 8 日至 10 月 11 日期间，在上海喜玛拉雅美术馆展出，感兴趣的不妨去现场看看。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203048PwMqIe8LYpuGCDrV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203048IG2Hpb5UqFcaeQYW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060520304931ZMboqNds5hAEup.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052030502Q7hCIxMSgeLRNEd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203050UzahgZ92FSA4ryxT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tCollection by CoverGirl &amp; Star Wars \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>“星战”年，彩妆也来凑热闹了。近日，美国彩妆品牌 CoverGirl 和 Star Wars 联手推出了一个彩妆系列，为即将上映的《星球大战 7：原力觉醒》造势，目前推出的包括睫毛膏、唇彩、唇膏、指甲油等产品，全部采用黑色或银色包装，上面印有 Star Wars 标识，看起来酷酷的。至于这套彩妆效果如何，相信不久就能看到女星战粉丝发回评价了。产品将于 9 月正式全线推出。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203056awt5D46YPcUF1MnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203057zx0CP6MGlZcJuHri.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203110B6iFbsfqxOZ9J0U8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203111lw9BuQrnHJbEoROy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052031119fEHuOK8PyecDTBr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tElectric Surf Board by Onean \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>很多人喜欢冲浪，但有时间条件限制，所在的地区可能没有成片的海水，而河水又难以满足他们肾上腺素飙升的感觉。于是，Onean 推出的这款电动冲浪滑板就是为他们体贴考虑后设计的，滑板采用电力，有足够的马力满足在河里冲浪的需求，同时，还有不同的马力可以选择。<a href=\"http://www.onean.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203112FsvSmRwQVYToBf8K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55745721\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203112W3M7SbHhw80NrPIp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203113JYS9ABNzqT4xsGuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203113ws7Ng1HQeV9LWPlk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203114bm5vf9uixBAeOXkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203114Xm64R2SM5dbjEhJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605203115n6dpB24CHtMXIwGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}